When it comes to enjoying a well-balanced lifestyle that promotes optimal nutrition and wellbeing of body and mind, compromising is never an option. We are a trusted and well-experienced company that focuses on delivering natural, affordable plant based powders which are meant to add taste and nutrients to your everyday life, without interfering with your comfort or safety. We rely only on natural, carefully selected ingredients and verified suppliers, in order to meet every customer’s rigorous quality expectations. Not entirely happy with one of our products? Make sure to tell us all about it and our customer care department will address the situation!

 Premium Organic Variety of Herbal Extracts – The Possibilities Are Endless

 These plant powders are available in 13 different varieties, containing only highest quality, natural, non-GMO herbs. Arriving in a convenient 20 gram pouch with a stand-alone base for easy storage and resealable design for preserved freshness, these plant extracts are highly versatile, being suitable for water-based shots, smoothies, cooking seasoning, as well as traditional teas or plant infusions.

 Not entirely convinced? Here are some of the amazing features of these plant based extracts:

 Many varieties available to choose from
 Organic and natural;
 Resealable 20 gram pouch for prolonged freshness;
 Nutrient rich selection of herbs and plants;
 Versatile uses;
 Original gift choice for friends, loved ones.

 Enjoy maximum nutritional intake with our premium, organic herbal powders!
 Pickup the 25 pack today! It is your next distribution opportunity.

